  <description><![CDATA[<p>Hotel Albolina offers excellent service, wine and food in one of Val di Fassa's peaceful villages, Alba. The slopes are a short walk away too, making it the perfect spot to explore the Val di Fassa region.</p>
<h2>Peaceful location</h2>
<p><span style="font-size: 14px;">Alba is a quiet town in the Val di Fassa region. There are some lovely local restaurants and cafes to try, if you are looking for lively après bars you can catch the bus into Canazei which has bars and shops a-plenty.</span></p>
<h2>Wine &amp; dine</h2>
<p>The hotel takes pride in their dishes and every day the hotel carefully selects the freshest produce. At dinner you can expect a four course served meal with traditional Ladin dishes popular in the <a data-udi="umb://document/4b1a446ce5904ac5997483a5477c9c8c" href="/{localLink:umb://document/4b1a446ce5904ac5997483a5477c9c8c}" title="Val di Fassa (Canazei, Campitello, Alba &amp; Penia)">Val di Fassa</a> region.</p>
<p>With over 2000 labels and bottles from different regions, the Hotel Albolina wine cellar is an experience in itself. Ask your waiter to recommend a local Italian wine with dinner, or you can try a multitude of different options during one of the hotel's wine tastings, available on request and payable locally.</p>
<h2>Easy slope access</h2>
<p>Hotel Albolina is just a seven minute walk from the Alba Ciampac gondola which gives you access to skiing on the Colac mountain.</p>
<p>Accessing the Sellaronda circuit is easy too. The ski bus stop is a two minute walk from the hotel with a regular service into Canazei. From here you can hop on the Belvedere gondola and experience some of the most incredible <a data-udi="umb://document/47c7f0773b104efb87f3357e7314f393" href="/{localLink:umb://document/47c7f0773b104efb87f3357e7314f393}" title="The Dolomites Ski Area">Dolomite</a> mountain views.</p>
<h3>Exclusive to Inghams</h3>
<p>As a ski specialist tour operator we carefully select the very best accommodation in our resorts and package them with flights and transfers, so that you can make the most of your holiday. We have an exclusive agreement with Hotel Albolina the only UK tour operator to package and sell holidays here - all the more reason to book with Inghams today!</p>]]></description>
